[B][SIZE="4"][center][img]https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CesiumOS-org/CesiumOS-Template/master/res/banner-v2-6-for-thread.png[/img]
Welcome to CesiumOS, yet another AOSP project. But this is one that will be a very different and exciting project. What differentiates us from the rest, you ask? Well that's why you're here - to find out.
[i][b]*Note[/b] This thread is optimised for both Light and Dark XDA themes. View this thread in a browser to have a magical experience![/i]:D

[img]https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CesiumOS-org/CesiumOS-Template/master/res/Cesium-Text-Banner-About-Us.png[/img]
CesiumOS is a project that is designed to be exciting. It is something that was born out of a sea of similar-looking AOSP roms. We offer a unique, yet familiar experience for your phone. We cherry-pick features that we think will [b]*actually*[/b] be useful in your daily lives, and nothing more. Since this is the beginning of something beautiful and exciting, we will continue to add more features in the future releases. We will strive to keep the ROM bloat-free, yet still have enough features that will keep you satisfied.

[img]https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CesiumOS-org/CesiumOS-Template/master/res/Cesium-Text-Banner-Features.png[/img]

[HIDE]
[code]
[b]STATUSBAR:[/b]
- Statusbar icons
- 4G icon instead of LTE
- Old style network indicators (Pre-P style)
- Battery indicator customization
- Status bar clock
- DT2S on status bar

[b]LOCKSCREEN:[/b]
- Fingerprint authentication vibration
- DT2S of lockscreen 
- Lockscreen shortcut customization 
- Pocket mode support
- Media art

[b]NAVIGATION & BUTTONS:[/b]
- Invert navbar
- Navbar layout
- Power menu customization 
- Playback control
- Screenoff torch 
- Volume panel location

[b]UI TUNER:[/b]
- QS Tile colors
- Brighness slider customizations 
- R style notification 
- Notification headers

[b]NOTFICATIONS:[/b]
- In call vibrations
- Battery light customization

[b]BATTERY:[/b]
- Aggersive mode 
- Smart Pixels

[b]EXTRAS:[/b]
- Three finger swipe to screenshot
- Incall vibrations 
- Signature spoofing
- Face Unlock
- Data switch tile
- Hide gesture pill
- A lot more ;)[/code]
[/HIDE]

